  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to identify and weight attributes of topic and systemic pain
      treatment options relevant from the patients' perspective with peripheral neuropathic pain.
      The study will use a discrete choice experimental design to reach its objective.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
